---
name: Bug Report
description: Create a report to help us improve the application.
title: "[BUG] - [Brief description of the bug]"
labels: bug
assignees: ''

body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        Please describe the bug you encountered. Include steps to reproduce, expected behavior, and actual behavior.

  - type: input
    id: steps-to-reproduce
    attributes:
      label: Steps to reproduce
      placeholder: "List the steps to reproduce the bug..."

  - type: input
    id: expected-behavior
    attributes:
      label: Expected behavior
      placeholder: "What did you expect to happen?"

  - type: input
    id: actual-behavior
    attributes:
      label: Actual behavior
      placeholder: "What actually happened?"

  - type: input
    id: additional-info
    attributes:
      label: Additional information
      placeholder: "Any other details that might help us..."

---

name: Feature Request
description: Suggest an idea for this project.
title: "[FEATURE] - [Brief description of the feature]"
labels: enhancement
assignees: ''

body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        Please describe your idea for a new feature. Include details about the functionality and why it would be beneficial.

  - type: input
    id: feature-description
    attributes:
      label: Feature description
      placeholder: "Describe the feature you would like to see..."

  - type: input
    id: use-case
    attributes:
      label: Use case
      placeholder: "How would this feature be used?"

  - type: input
    id: additional-info
    attributes:
      label: Additional information
      placeholder: "Any other details that might help us..."